   <h1 class="thd_title">北京市65周岁及以上老年人优待卡有关问答</h1> 
   <span class="thd_time">2013-11-01&nbsp; &nbsp;</span> 
   <div class="thd_doc box"> 
    <div style="width:450px; margin:0 auto;" class="tupian"></div> 
    <div id="TRS_AUTOADD_1388899649171">
     <style id="_Custom_V6_Style_">

